                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="4r" to="6r"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="LIT1716Kidanz">ኪዳን፡ ዘነግህ፡</title>
                        <note>
                           The text follows a short invocation to Our Lady Mary: 
                           <q xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡ እምነ፡ ወእሙ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ሰዓሊ፡ በእንቲአነ፡ ከመ፡ ይምሃረነ፡ ወይሣሃለነ፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ወ</supplied>ያስተርኢ፡ ኂሩቱ፡ 
                              በላዕሌነ፡</q>.
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="6v" to="8v"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="">መስተብቍዕ፡ ዘሐዋርያት፡</title>
                        <note>
                           <!-- Prayers for the sick, the pilgrims, the rain, the fruits of the earth, the water of the rivers, the king, the offerers, the sleepers, the catechumens, the peace</title>
                              <! Cp. the same prayers are also found in the following mss: 
                              BAVet1#ms_i4.9, BAVet15#p2_i4.2, BAVet18#ms_i6.7, BAVet22#ms_i3.1, BAVet69#ms_i3, BAVet88#ms_i3, BLadd16202#ms_i1.2 > -->
                        </note>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           ናስተበቍዕ፡ ዘኵሎ፡ ይእኅዝ፡ እግዚአብ<supplied reason="omitted">ሔር</supplied>፡ አብ፡ ለእግዚእ<supplied reason="omitted">ነ</supplied>፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ 
                           ኢየሱስ፡ <choice><sic>ክርስትስ፡</sic><corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ክርስቶስ፡</corr></choice> እንዘ፡ 
                           <choice><sic>ነአኵት፡</sic></choice> በኵሉ፡ ወበውስተ፡ ኵሉ፡ እስመ፡ ከደነነ፡  <choice><sic>ወረደአነ፡</sic></choice> ሶቀነ፡ ወአብጽሐነ፡ እስከ፡ 
                           <choice><sic>ዘቲ፡</sic></choice> ሰዓት፡
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           እንዘ፡ ነሐዩ፡ በኵሉ፡ አምልኮ፡ ሠናይ፡ በፈሪሃ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወበኂ<add place="above">ሩ</add>ት፡ ንትረከብ፡ በክርስቶስ፡ ዘቦቱ፡ <gap reason="omitted" extent="unknown" resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/>
                        </explicit>
